\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>주요 영단어나 표현 정리</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>fast-forward : 미국식은 ㅐ 발음이지만, f 이후 ㅏ 발음으로 읽는다.</li>\n<li>The compony has a strong track record of …</li>\n<li>Let me share with you…</li>\n<li>The Imperial Lemon’s key strengths are …</li>\n<li>위의 세 표현은 발표 시 전형적으로 사용할 법한 표현 문구다. 틀은 기억해두자.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#introduction\">Introduction</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#the-imperial-lemon\">The Imperial Lemon</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94-%EC%98%81%EB%8B%A8%EC%96%B4%EB%82%98-%ED%91%9C%ED%98%84-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\">주요 영단어나 표현 정리</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"June 20, 2022","title":"13_The Imperial Lemon","categories":"study","author":"Paul","emoji":"🇱🇷🇮🇸"},"fields":{"slug":"/STUDY/english_talking/20220620_13_The Imperial Lemon/"}},"prev":null,"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://paul2021-r.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"Paul2021-R/Paul2021-R.github.io"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/STUDY/english_talking/20220620_14_Telephone tell-tale/","nextSlug":"/STUDY/english_talking/20220620_13_The Imperial Lemon/","prevSlug":""}},
